text: Greve Fodbold is a Danish football club currently playing in the Danmarksserien. They play at Greve Idræts Center in Greve on Zealand, which has a capacity of 7,000. ==Notable managers== *Sten Ziegler *Karsten Aabrink *Jan Kalborg *Morten Eskesen (2006–2009) *Jesper Hansen (2010) *Anders Sundstrup (2010–2011) *Anders Jochumsen (2011) *Jesper Falck (2011) *Finn M.
